## Summary of Changes

- `src/structured/validateJsonSchema.ts`: Added `const`, `not`, `anyOf`, `oneOf`, `allOf`, `$defs`/`$ref` (local only, circular detection), string `format` (date/date-time/email/uri/uuid/ipv4/ipv6). New helpers: `ResolveContext`, `deepEqual`, `FORMAT_PATTERNS`.
- `src/structured/providerFormats.ts`: New module — `buildOpenAIResponseFormat`, `buildOllamaFormat`, `buildGeminiResponseSchema`.
- `src/structured/index.ts`: Added `providerFormats.js` barrel export.
- 82 new tests; 327 total passing. PR #32.
